{"tid":626801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【窮人新定義】「窮人恩物」呎價直逼1.9萬 1房逼6球","createTime":"2018-04-12T12:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T05:48:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab70af27c6f191159b24e641dca4f3baef804bf","tid":626801,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180412/large/1523531789_c8f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F1523531789_c8f2.jpg&h=8d25750d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣「楊屋道三寶」連環破頂。消息指，爵悅庭北爵軒高層H室，實用面積1,045方呎，成交價1,450萬元，呎價13,876元，樓價創屋苑歷史新高。賣方2006年以582萬元買入，賬面獲利868萬元，升值1.5倍。<br />\n<br />\n另一單破頂是昔日「窮人恩物」樂悠居，呎價直逼1.9萬元。消息指高層18室，實用面積312方呎，成交價585萬元，呎價18,750元創屋苑歷史新高。原業主2013年以360萬元買入，賺225萬元或63%。<br />\n2012年初網絡瘋傳一張物業宣傳單張，形容樂悠居為「窮人恩物」，一個建築面積753方呎(實用面積538方呎)、叫價410萬元的單位為「窮人恩物」。當時被一眾網民挖苦代理為窮人寫下新定義，買唔起4球樓連窮人都冇資格做。6年後的今天，「窮人恩物」1房都升到近600萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180412/large/1523530863_70c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F1523530863_70c3.jpg&h=db8cbf24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180412/58065055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58065055&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=6d6e3cd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F58065055&h=04fed8b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180412/58065055</a>"},{"pid":"871b29fb7908f7d0c70f8e82bc22014186f10e9a","tid":626801,"uid":125470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:15:00.000Z","msg":"今時今日賣樓無得賺 發展商但求打個和 大家開開心心有屋住架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554cee4e8b64f2c933b39757baa0d8693612e4be","tid":626801,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"871b29fb7908f7d0c70f8e82bc22014186f10e9a","tid":626801,"uid":125470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:15:00.000Z","msg":"今時今日賣樓無得賺 發展商但求打個和 大家開開心心有屋住架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a31b81711a4f6857ff9a8d2b6a06e7390eed541","tid":626801,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e43ab77b7611f2164b1b08b61b9190c67a47713","tid":626801,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"人工升左幾多又唔講"},{"pid":"539dc49be46b5058cbe5d27c0ed1fc004fb84264","tid":626801,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35f1bba01a2c266392e1514531ccfe8c34dee99a","tid":626801,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292fa927a4d52e3333741b671552e98b791c972b","tid":626801,"uid":43173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"黃子華：300呎豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de63d6c6fb8d196e32900f7cd4ea1076c647f4b","tid":626801,"uid":78165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"連窮人都冇資格做<img src=\"/ass